{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|1Co|12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","chapter":12,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":1,"text":"Now concerning spiritual gifts: brothers and sisters, I do not want you to be unaware.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":2,"text":"You know that when you were pagans, you used to be enticed and led astray by mute idols.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":3,"text":"Therefore I want you to know that no one speaking by the Spirit of God says, “Jesus is cursed,” and no one can say, “Jesus is Lord,” except by the Holy Spirit.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":4,"text":"Now there are different gifts, but the same Spirit.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":5,"text":"There are different ministries, but the same Lord.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":6,"text":"And there are different activities, but the same God works all of them in each person.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":7,"text":"A manifestation of the Spirit is given to each person for the common good:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":8,"text":"to one is given a message of wisdom through the Spirit, to another, a message of knowledge by the same Spirit,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":9,"text":"to another, faith by the same Spirit, to another, gifts of healing by the one Spirit,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":10,"text":"to another, the performing of miracles, to another, prophecy, to another, distinguishing between spirits, to another, different kinds of tongues, to another, interpretation of tongues.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":11,"text":"One and the same Spirit is active in all these, distributing to each person as he wills.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":12,"text":"For just as the body is one and has many parts, and all the parts of that body, though many, are one body —so also is Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":13,"text":"For we were all baptized by one Spirit into one body —whether Jews or Greeks, whether slaves or free —and we were all given one Spirit to drink.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":14,"text":"Indeed, the body is not one part but many.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":15,"text":"If the foot should say, “Because I’m not a hand, I don’t belong to the body,” it is not for that reason any less a part of the body.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":16,"text":"And if the ear should say, “Because I’m not an eye, I don’t belong to the body,” it is not for that reason any less a part of the body.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":17,"text":"If the whole body were an eye, where would the hearing be? If the whole body were an ear, where would the sense of smell be?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":18,"text":"But as it is, God has arranged each one of the parts in the body just as he wanted.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":19,"text":"And if they were all the same part, where would the body be?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":20,"text":"As it is, there are many parts, but one body.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":21,"text":"The eye cannot say to the hand, “I don’t need you!” Or again, the head can’t say to the feet, “I don’t need you!”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":22,"text":"On the contrary, those parts of the body that are weaker are indispensable.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":23,"text":"And those parts of the body that we consider less honorable, we clothe these with greater honor, and our unrespectable parts are treated with greater respect,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":24,"text":"which our respectable parts do not need.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":25,"text":"so that there would be no division in the body, but that the members would have the same concern for each other.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":26,"text":"So if one member suffers, all the members suffer with it; if one member is honored, all the members rejoice with it.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":27,"text":"Now you are the body of Christ, and individual members of it.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":28,"text":"And God has appointed these in the church: first apostles, second prophets, third teachers, next miracles, then gifts of healing, helping, leading, various kinds of tongues.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":29,"text":"Are all apostles? Are all prophets? Are all teachers? Do all do miracles?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:30","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":30,"text":"Do all have gifts of healing? Do all speak in tongues? Do all interpret?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:31","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":12,"verse":31,"text":"But desire the greater gifts. And I will show you an even better way.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","chapter":12,"paragraphStarts":[1,4,12,25,27],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Diversity of Spiritual Gifts"},{"beforeVerse":12,"text":"Unity Yet Diversity in the Body"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now concerning spiritual gifts: "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or spiritual things, or spiritual people"},{"kind":"text","text":" brothers and sisters, I do not want you to be unaware. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or spiritual things, or spiritual people"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You know that when you were pagans, you used to be enticed and led astray by mute "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:32","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":32,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 14:10","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 2:16","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" idols. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 8:4","book":"1Co","chapter":8,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 8:32","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":32},{"label":"1Co 14:10","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":10},{"label":"2Pt 2:16","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":16},{"label":"1Co 8:4","book":"1Co","chapter":8,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore I want you to know that no one speaking by the Spirit of God says, “Jesus is cursed,” and no one can say, “Jesus is Lord,” except by the Holy Spirit."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now there are different gifts, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 12:6","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 14:1","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:8","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 2:4","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 4:10","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":10,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" but the same Spirit. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 12:6","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":6},{"label":"1Co 14:1","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":1},{"label":"Eph 4:8","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":8},{"label":"Heb 2:4","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"1Pt 4:10","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"There are different ministries, but the same Lord. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And there are different activities, but the same God works all of them in each person. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"A manifestation of the Spirit is given to each person "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 4:5","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the common good: "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jms 4:5","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"to one "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 12:7–8","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:11","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 4:11","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" is given a message of wisdom "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 2:6–7","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" through the Spirit, to another, a message of knowledge by the same Spirit, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 12:7–8","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":7},{"label":"Eph 4:11","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":11},{"label":"1Pt 4:11","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":11},{"label":"1Co 2:6–7","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"to another, faith by the same Spirit, to another, gifts of healing "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 13:32","book":"Luk","chapter":13,"verse":32,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:22","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:30","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":30,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:38","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":38,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" by the one Spirit, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 13:32","book":"Luk","chapter":13,"verse":32},{"label":"Ac 4:22","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":22},{"label":"Ac 4:30","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":30},{"label":"Ac 10:38","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":38}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"to another, the performing of miracles, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 19:11","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" to another, prophecy, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 13:2","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to another, distinguishing between spirits, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 4:1–3","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" to another, different kinds of tongues, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"languages"},{"kind":"text","text":" to another, interpretation of tongues. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 19:11","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":11},{"label":"1Co 13:2","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":2},{"label":"1Jn 4:1–3","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"languages"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"One and the same Spirit is active in all these, distributing to each person as he wills."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For just as the body is one "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 11:52","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":52,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and has many parts, and all the parts of that body, though many, are one body —so also is Christ. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:4","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 11:52","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":52},{"label":"Eph 4:4","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For we were all baptized by "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or with, or in"},{"kind":"text","text":" one Spirit into one body —whether Jews or Greeks, whether slaves or free —and we were all given one Spirit to drink. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:28","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:13–18","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:11","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gl 3:28","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":28},{"label":"Eph 2:13–18","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":13},{"label":"Col 3:11","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or with, or in"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Indeed, the body is not one part but many. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If the foot should say, “Because I’m not a hand, I don’t belong to the body,” it is not for that reason any less a part of the body. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And if the ear should say, “Because I’m not an eye, I don’t belong to the body,” it is not for that reason any less a part of the body. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If the whole body were an eye, where would the hearing be? If the whole body were an ear, where would the sense of smell be? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But as it is, God has arranged each one of the parts in the body just as he wanted. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 143:10","book":"Psa","chapter":143,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 16:9","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 5:30","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":30,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:4","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:9","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:17","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":17,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 143:10","book":"Psa","chapter":143,"verse":10},{"label":"Pr 16:9","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":9},{"label":"Jn 5:30","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":30},{"label":"Gl 1:4","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":4},{"label":"Eph 1:9","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":9},{"label":"1Jn 2:17","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And if they were all the same part, where would the body be? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"As it is, there are many parts, but one body. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The eye cannot say to the hand, “I don’t need you!” Or again, the head can’t say to the feet, “I don’t need you!” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On the contrary, those parts of the body that are weaker are indispensable. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And those parts of the body that we consider less honorable, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 6:4","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:7","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" we clothe these with greater honor, and our unrespectable parts are treated with greater respect, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 6:4","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":4},{"label":"1Pt 2:7","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"which our respectable parts do not need."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"so that there would be no division "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:10","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the body, but that the members would have the same concern for each other. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 1:10","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So if one member suffers, all the members suffer with it; if one member is honored, all the members rejoice with it."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now you are the body of Christ, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:23","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:18","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and individual members of it. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 1:23","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":23},{"label":"Col 1:18","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And God has appointed these in the church: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 16:18","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 14:4","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 1:4","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" first apostles, second prophets, third teachers, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:11","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":11,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 3:1","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":1,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" next miracles, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 13:22","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":22,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" then gifts of healing, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 12:9","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":9,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" helping, leading, various kinds of tongues. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"languages, also in v. 30"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 16:18","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":18},{"label":"1Co 14:4","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":4},{"label":"Rv 1:4","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":4},{"label":"Eph 4:11","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":11},{"label":"Jms 3:1","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":1},{"label":"Mk 13:22","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":22},{"label":"1Co 12:9","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"languages, also in v. 30"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Are all apostles? Are all prophets? Are all teachers? Do all do miracles? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Do all have gifts of healing? Do all speak in tongues? Do all interpret? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 24:27","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":27,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 24:27","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:12:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But desire "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 25:13","book":"Num","chapter":25,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 4:2","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" the greater gifts. And I will show you an even better way."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 25:13","book":"Num","chapter":25,"verse":13},{"label":"Jms 4:2","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279659983}